4.
 Compliance and Exceptions
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Mandatory Enforcement
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Personnel and systems must comply with the requirements defined herein.
 Failure to comply shall result in one or more of the following enforcement actions:
 (a) immediate isolation of the non-compliant system from the network;
 (b) revocation of user access privileges;
 (c) disciplinary action up to and including termination of employment.
\end_layout

